OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDrivers to be banned from  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fusing hand-held devices    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, UK drivers will be banned from filming 
OL,6, or searching playlists on hand-held    
OL,7, devices from next year under government
OL,8, plans to toughen road safety laws.     
OL,10,FIt is already illegal to call or text  
OL,11,Fon hand-held phones while driving      
OL,12,Funless it is an emergency.             
OL,14,FFrom 2022, drivers will be barred from 
OL,15,Fusing a device to take photos or play  
OL,16,Fgames - with rule-breakers facing a    
OL,17,F#200 fine and six licence points.      
OL,19,FThe transport secretary said it  would 
OL,20,Fbe easier to prosecute offenders.      
